This paper is about object detection using deep learning, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new approach for object detection, which involves utilizing convolutional feature interrelationship, and this is a topic that falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the speed and performance of the proposed approach, which are topics that fall under neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
